      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEBON DISCO (7) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last five runs. Last time finished 2nd over 342m at Angle Park beaten 5 lengths (19.84) behind Brindle Benny in a Other on March 24. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Top chance in this line up. BEN LIKES SCOTCH (8) tends to drift back and work into the race, finishing out of the placings two back before charging home into the minors latest when third (23.08) in a Grade 6/MDN at this track last time. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Expected to be in the finish again. LOCKABA ROCKET (4) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.37) in a Other at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. In the mix. SIGNIFICANT (2) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can turn the form around.",
